CLEAN-ROOM NOTICE
-----------------
Uni-UI is an independent, clean-room implementation. It depends only on
permissively licensed (MIT / Apache-2.0 / BSD / Zlib) crates and contains no
source copied from GPL/copyleft projects — including, explicitly, none of
Slint's `i-slint-*` crates — and none from any proprietary framework. Any
language or API surface it accepts (e.g. importers) is reconstructed from
public documentation only.

Third-party permissive components retain their own licenses; their required
attribution / NOTICE accompanies distributed builds.

